" ============================================================
"  Cyberpunk Tridactyl Config — tridactylrc
"  Replicates qutebrowser keybinds and behavior in Firefox.
"  Reload with: :source
" ============================================================

" --- Theme ---
colorscheme cyberpunk

" --- General settings ---
set smoothscroll true
set hintchars asdfghjkl
set editorcmd kitty -e vim %f
set newtab about:blank

" --- Search engines (matching qutebrowser) ---
set searchurls.DEFAULT https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s
set searchurls.aw https://wiki.archlinux.org/?search=%s
set searchurls.apkg https://archlinux.org/packages/?sort=&q=%s&maintainer=&flagged=
set searchurls.gh https://github.com/search?o=desc&q=%s&s=stars
set searchurls.yt https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s

" --- Keybinds: Navigation (qutebrowser parity) ---

" = to open URL/search (like qutebrowser)
bind = fillcmdline open

" h for history
bind h fillcmdline open -b history

" T to hint links in new tab
bind T hint -t

" Open clipboard URL in current tab / new tab
bind pp clipboard open
bind pt clipboard tabopen

" Tab movement
bind gJ tabmove +1
bind gK tabmove -1

" --- Keybinds: UI Toggles ---

" tH — toggle tab bar visibility
bind tH guiset_quiet tabs toggle

" sH — toggle navigation bar
bind sH guiset_quiet navbar toggle

" --- Keybinds: Extras ---

" d to close tab (qutebrowser default)
bind d tabclose

" u to undo close tab
bind u undo

" Shift+H / Shift+L for back/forward
bind H back
bind L forward

" J / K to switch tabs
bind J tabprev
bind K tabnext

" gi to focus first input field
bind gi focusinput -l

" yy to yank current URL
bind yy clipboard yank

" --- Disable Tridactyl on certain sites ---
" (sites where you want normal key behavior)
autocmd DocStart mail.google.com mode ignore
autocmd DocStart docs.google.com mode ignore
autocmd DocStart sheets.google.com mode ignore
autocmd DocStart discord.com mode ignore

" --- Privacy ---
" Block canvas fingerprinting notification
set csp csp

" --- Hint mode styling is in themes/cyberpunk.css ---
